    textOverlay: "I tried every spiritual practice that was trending. Manifestation journals, crystal healing, sound baths, moon rituals. Most of them did nothing. Here's what actually shifted something:\n\nMeditation — but not the pretty Instagram kind. The boring, sit-with-your-thoughts, want-to-quit-after-2-minutes kind. Consistency over perfection.\n\nGratitude — not listing random things. Deeply FEELING grateful for one specific thing each morning. Really sitting in it.\n\nSolitude — turning off my phone and being alone with myself for an hour. We're so afraid of silence that we never hear our own wisdom.\n\nService — doing something for someone else with zero expectation of return. This one rewired my brain faster than anything.\n\nSpiritual growth isn't about crystals and sage. It's about getting honest with yourself and doing the uncomfortable work.",
